Package org.sebastiandine.cardcollectionmanager.container

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBeanContainer
    This abstract class acts as a template for container classes, which manage CardCollectionBean implementing objects.
    CardBeanContainer
    This container class provides holds a list of CardBean objects and provides methods for interaction with this list.
    SetBeanContainer
    This container class provides holds a list of SetBean objects and provides methods for interaction with this list.
